ht mode, breathing mode, heartbeat mode, flash-on-clash mode and blaster function included.', '✘FX Saber Support Real Heavy Dueling - Premium aluminum hilt and durable blade makes the saber suitable for fans heavy dueling. High-impact Polycarbonate blade, saber total 44in Long.', '✘Infinite Color Changing - Preset Colors with White, Bright White, Yellow, Orange, Purple, Pink, Light Pink, Hot Pink, Cyan, Light Cyan, Light Purple, Green, Teal, Red, Light Blue, Dark Blue. Many color options to choose from and switch on the go.']
